      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just... too quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i still expect to see him sitting there, but it's just nothing. it's like i'm just a ghost moving through a house that doesn't belong to me anymore. i don't even know why i bother getting out of bed. what is the point of all this just being alone?",
