      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what \"purpose\"? everything just feels so hollow. it's like i'm just performing these little rituals—making coffee, checking the mail, going to work—but none of it actually matters because the person i did it all for isn't here. it's not about \"moving forward,\" it feels more like i'm just dragging this heavy, useless weight around for no reason at all. it's just exhausting.",
