      "content": "just \"staying afloat\"... is that really it? to just exist in this state of constant, heavy nothingness until I die? it feels so cruel that the world just keeps moving while mine stopped. sometimes i look at the empty spot next to me in bed and i just think... maybe it would be easier if i wasn't even here to feel the silence. it wouldn't be so much work if i didn't have to fight to breathe every single day.",
